job.title: Software Engineer
job.description: Software Engineer Partner Software - Athens, GA Partner Software is seeking a Mid-Level Full Stack Developer/Engineer for the Map Platform team. We are looking for a motivated developer who wants to own the design and development of an application used to process, analyze, and display geographic data. If you have a desire to take lead on a project and build simple yet powerful programs, you will be a great fit. You will also enjoy the benefits of working in a small and fast paced business that is backed with the necessary resources to enhance your career and have your efforts play a key role in the success of the company. What We Are Looking For 2+ years experience in Java development Excellent analytical and problem solving skills Strong communication skills and the ability to work closely with others Demonstrated ability to work on small, focused teams What Will Help You Stand Out Experience with GIS Experience with code versioning tools and process
